---
title: Quick Bacon, Tomato & Pesto Trottole with Radish Salad & Parmesan
description: Presenting a few of our favourite things: rich tomato sauce, bacon, Parmesan cheese and basil pesto. All of those deep flavours meld together wonderfully when tossed through spirals of trottole. Along with a crunchy radish salad, this'll be bumped up to a champion household dinner in no time!

*Keep an eye out... Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced fusilli with trottole and tinned cherry tomatoes with chopped tomatoes, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
